title: Rewards?
body: Hello, I finished the season at S5 but didn't get the border or the icon, I'm not sure if all the rewards were given out yet or not.

replies.body: All of the rewards hadn't been delivered quite yet when you posted this, but you should have them now! Let me know if you still don't see your rewards though and I can take a look.

I still haven't received the rewards yet, I'm not sure if they were all distributed or not. I got the preseason rewards but not the end of season stuff like the Silver border or the icon. Should I take it up with the support?
